title: Terra Formars Gaiden: Onizuka Keiji
original_name: テラフォーマーズ外伝 鬼塚慶次
sinopse:
You will know the man, the boxer, Keiji Onizuka.

Before Annex 1 sets out for Mars, Keiji is stationed in U-NASA's branch office in Japan undergoing training. What unknown incident will he be pulled into?

(Source: ANN)
